    say("Task-spec quality checklist:")
    say("- Choose and announce one explicit configured difficulty before creation.")
    say("- One clear outcome.")
    say("- Observable acceptance criteria.")
    say("- Only needed paths and context.")
    say("- Exact targeted verification commands.")
